name: Secret of Googol 7: Eggs All Around: Egg Trek: Balloon Picnic
overview: The Secret of Googol: Eggs All Around 7 - Egg Trek / Balloon Picnic is a Miscellaneous game, developed and published by Lightspan, which was released in 1997. Welcome to The Secret of Googol, where your child uses mathematics skills to help Cali and Wigsley run an egg factory and plan a company picnic.
